List all apps with:
$ pm list packages

To uninstall apps, run:
$ pm uninstall -k --user 0 NAME_OF_APP

To just disable apps, run:
$ pm disable-user --user 0 NAME_OF_APP

To re-install apps, run:
$ pm package install-existing NAME_OF_APP

Tu re-enable apps, run:
$ pm enable NAME_OF_APP

# SOME APPS THAT CAN BE REMOVED/DISABLED: #

# Mi Picks - also known as GetApps:
com.xiaomi.mipicks

# Youtube - bloated with ads:
com.google.android.youtube

# Google Search:
com.google.android.googlequicksearchbox

# Facebook:
com.facebook.katana
com.facebook.system
com.facebook.appmanager
com.facebook.services

# Microsoft Office:
com.microsoft.office.excel
com.microsoft.office.powerpoint
com.microsoft.office.onenote
com.microsoft.office.skydrive

# Skype:
com.skype.raide 
